decode(int) - Method in class squidpony.performance.alternate.NextDijkstraMap

decodeX(int) - Method in class squidpony.performance.alternate.NextDijkstraMap

decodeY(int) - Method in class squidpony.performance.alternate.NextDijkstraMap
If you for some reason have one of the internally-used ints produced by NextDijkstraMap.encode(Coord), this will decode the y component of the point encoded in that int.
deteriorate(List<Coord>) - Method in class squidpony.performance.alternate.DijkstraMap
Used in conjunction with methods that depend on finding cover, like findCoveredAttackPath(), this method causes specified risky points to be considered less safe, and will encourage a pathfinder to keep moving toward a goal instead of just staying in cover forever (or until an enemy moves around the cover and ambushes the pathfinder).
